.unauth-app__background { background: linear-gradient(77.34deg, rgb(211, 220, 250) -5.81%, rgba(243, 246, 255, 0) 81.57%), linear-gradient(85.83deg, rgba(243, 246, 255, 0.2) 49.81%, rgba(243, 246, 255, 0) 78.82%), radial-gradient(55.02% 39.81% at 31.38% 48.82%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7) 0px, rgba(245, 248, 254, 0) 92.98%); transform: translateY(-94px) rotate(90deg); position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100vw; z-index: -1; }
